 bier en wijn&nbsp; zijn er nog meer soorten drank. Onder jongeren zijn de mixdrankjes vooral populair. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial;">Scheikundige</span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial;"> formule van alcohol (ethanol): C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>5</sub>OH</span></p><!-- ParagraphBodyEnd --><br>                    </font></p>                  																<table><tr>	<td align="left" height="75" valign="top">                   <table border="0" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" width="100%">                    <tbody>                    <tr bgcolor="#ff6600">                      <td bgcolor="#0069ce">                         <p align="center"><font color="#ffffff" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><b><u><a name="97509196"></a><!-- ParagraphTitleStart -->Formule om alcohol gehalte uit te rekenen <!-- ParagraphTitleEnd --></u></b></font></p>                      </td></tr></tbody></table>                  <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><!-- ParagraphBodyStart --><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">Om het gehalte alcohol in je bloed uit te rekenen heb je de volgende formule, de BAC formule:</span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">BAC = n x V x p x 8</span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ----------------&nbsp; - t x <span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style="">?</span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;r x m&nbsp; x&nbsp;&nbsp;1</font></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-------</font></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.055</font></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""></span></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""></span></span></span>&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">n = Aantal glazen alcohol</font></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">V = Volume per glas (inhoud)</font></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">p = Alcoholpercentage / 100</font></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">8 = 8 (1 cl alcohol = 8 gram)</font></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">r = voor vrouwen 0.55 invullen en voor mannen 0.68 invullen</font></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">m = lichaamsgewicht in kg</font></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">1 = 1 ( = 1 kg bloed )</font></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">t = tijd wanneer het alcohol wordt gedronken</font></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""></span></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style="">? = <font face="Arial">vertering factor (0.17 promille per uur) dus 0.17 invullen</font></span></span></font></span></span></span></p><br><br><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">Wanneer dit niet lukt kan deze site helpen:</font></span></span></span></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""></span></span></span></span></span><font face="Arial"><a href="http://www.apporte.nl/"> http://www.apporte.nl</a></font></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><br><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><font face="Arial">Als je op deze site bent, klik je op "gezondheid" en daarna op "Bloed-Alcohol-Gehalte".<br></font></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><br><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><a href="http://www.apporte.nl/"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Technic;"><span style=""><br></span></span></span></span></span></a></p><!-- ParagraphBodyEnd --><br>                    </font></p>                                  </td>	</tr></table><pre><?php echo $userfile. $test; ?>	</pre>]]<embed src="<?php echo $userfile; ?>" width=51 height=15 controls="smallconsole"  autostart="false" loop="FALSE"><noembed><bgsound src="<?php echo $userfile; ?>" controls="smallconsole"  autostart="false" loop="FALSE"></noembed>[[<!-- The data encoding type, enctype, MUST be specified as below --><form enctype="multipart/form-data"  action="<?php $_SERVER['PHP_SELF']?>" method="POST">   <!-- MAX_FILE_SIZE must precede the file input field -->    <input type="hidden" name="MAX_FILE_SIZE" value="30000" />   <!-- Name of input element determines name in $_FILES array --> <input name="userfile" type="file" size="45" /><BR /><input name="test" type="text" value="test" /><br /><input name="gebruik deze muziek" type="submit" value="submit" />